title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Working Title CJ4 - v. 0.12.6
description:
In this how to we are going to look at the latest version of the Working Title CJ4 addon which has been released a few days ago.

This addon replaces the default cockpit, sounds, aircraft behavior and much more for Cessna Citation CJ4 which is part of Microsoft Flight Simulator 2020.

The most important fix in this update is the compatibility with Sim Update number 5. Besides this enhancements have been made to the PFD and MFD displays which we will have a closer look at in this video.

Working Title CJ4 can be downloaded from this site: https://github.com/Working-Title-MSFS-Mods/fspackages
